01:54:00.920 --> 01:54:04.780
forget it.

01:54:04.780 --> 01:54:06.780
Bye.

01:54:06.780 --> 01:54:08.780
Are you okay?

01:54:08.780 --> 01:54:10.780
Yeah. Are you okay?

01:54:10.780 --> 01:54:17.960
Oh, I hope you made it.

01:54:17.960 --> 01:54:20.280
Who?

01:54:20.280 --> 01:54:27.100
A friend.

01:54:27.100 --> 01:54:28.100
Why did you come?

01:54:28.100 --> 01:54:30.100
I was worried about you.

01:54:30.100 --> 01:54:34.340
I care about you.

01:54:34.340 --> 01:54:36.340
I care about you, too.

01:54:36.340 --> 01:54:38.340
And for a long time, I...

01:54:38.340 --> 01:54:41.340
just didn't know how to say it.

01:54:41.340 --> 01:54:57.610
What changed your mind?

01:54:57.610 --> 01:54:59.610
Why did that happen?

01:54:59.610 --> 01:55:01.610
Because he made it.

01:55:01.610 --> 01:55:03.610
He got promoted to captain. He survived.

01:55:03.610 --> 01:55:29.880
For a long time, I wanted to tell you how much I cared about you.

01:55:29.880 --> 01:55:31.880
I just didn't have the words.

01:55:31.880 --> 01:55:36.180
Maybe this can say it for me.

01:55:36.180 --> 01:55:55.660
Jimmy checked the history book that the antique dealer had given him.

01:55:55.660 --> 01:55:58.660
The paragraph about William had changed.

01:55:58.660 --> 01:56:00.660
It said that he made it to Harrisville,

01:56:00.660 --> 01:56:02.660
proved his love to Emily,

01:56:02.660 --> 01:56:04.660
and married her.

01:56:04.660 --> 01:56:06.660
As for Jimmy and April,

01:56:06.660 --> 01:56:10.660
well, I'll let you figure that one out for yourselves.

01:56:10.660 --> 01:56:12.660
The end.

01:56:12.660 --> 01:56:13.660
Cool.

01:56:13.660 --> 01:56:16.660
I guess history can be interesting.

01:56:16.660 --> 01:56:22.050
Yeah, I guess.

01:56:22.050 --> 01:56:25.050
I've got a couple of tickets to the Phantasmagoria concert.

01:56:25.050 --> 01:56:27.050
I was wondering if maybe you and I could...

01:56:27.050 --> 01:56:29.050
I'm sorry.

01:56:29.050 --> 01:56:32.050
She's already going with me.

01:56:32.050 --> 01:56:33.050
And me.

01:56:33.050 --> 01:56:35.050
I had three tickets.

01:56:35.050 --> 01:56:40.410
So, Lace?

01:56:40.410 --> 01:57:50.900
Yes, that means, uh, your history.

01:57:50.900 --> 01:57:56.420
It is over.

01:57:56.420 --> 01:58:00.420
We'll be back in just 166 hours and counting.

